notes.title: Note
notes.description: The notes provided by Seriumium are temporary notepads that are stored as an INT integer with a maximum ID value of 9999. This note is overwritten when another user adds a note with the same ID, and is not an endlessly valid note because it is deleted when update. Seriumium is not responsible for the contents of this note.
